HEADWORD: Arboriculture
<hw>Ar`bor*i*cul"ture</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>arbor</ets> tree + <ets>cultura</ets>. See <er>Culture</er>.]</ety>
<def>The cultivation of trees and shrubs, chiefly for timber or for
ornamental purposes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

